da / For The Times</div>  <div class="trb_embed_related_caption">Walter Dean Myers, who died Tuesday, is shown in 1997 in his Jersey City, N.J., neighborhood.</div>  <div class="trb_embed_related_credit_and_caption" >Walter Dean Myers, who died Tuesday, is shown in 1997 in his Jersey City, N.J., neighborhood. (Stan Honda / For The Times)</div><div class="trb_socialize" data-role="socialshare_information socialshare_container" data-socialshare-context="page" data-socialshare-url="/books/jacketcopy/la-fe-jc-walter-dean-myers-has-died-20140702-001-photo.html" data-socialshare-title="Author Myers in New Jersey" data-socialshare-thumbnail="http://www.trbimg.com/img-53b45bb2/turbine/la-fe-jc-walter-dean-myers-has-died-20140702-001" data-socialshare-description="Walter Dean Myers, who died Tuesday, is shown in 1997 in his Jersey City, N.J., neighborhood." data-socialshare-slug="la-fe-jc-walter-dean-myers-has-died-20140702-001" data-socialshare-content="photo" data-socialshare-newspapername="Los Angeles Times" data-socialshare-content-id="80703668"  data-socialshare-default-image=""><span class="trb_socialize_item" data-role="socialshare_share " data-socialshare-type="facebook"         ></span><span class="trb_socialize_item" data-role="socialshare_share " data-socialshare-type="twitter"         ></span><span class="trb_socialize_item" data-role="socialshare_shareParent base_expandablemenu " data-socialshare-type="shareParent"         ><div class="trb_socialize_submenu"        ><span class="trb_socialize_item" data-role="socialshare_share" data-socialshare-type="pinterest"></span        ><span class="trb_socialize_item" data-role="socialshare_share" data-socialshare-type="googleplus"></span        ><span class="trb_socialize_item" data-role="socialshare_share" data-socialshare-type="linkedin"></span        ><span class="trb_socialize_item" data-role="socialshare_share" data-socialshare-type="stumbleupon"></span        ><span class="trb_socialize_item" data-role="socialshare