-military-interventions/16009002-topic.html">International Military Interventions</a><a class="trb_article_relatedTopics_a" title="Wars and Interventions" href="/topic/unrest-conflicts-war/wars-interventions/16009000-topic.html">Wars and Interventions</a><a class="trb_article_relatedTopics_a" title="Vietnam War (1955-1975)" href="/topic/unrest-conflicts-war/wars-interventions/vietnam-war-%281955-1975%29-EVHST000189-topic.html">Vietnam War (1955-1975)</a><a class="trb_article_relatedTopics_a" title="U.S. Army" href="/topic/unrest-conflicts-war/defense/u.s.-army-ORGOV0000126141142-topic.html">U.S. Army</a></div></div>                                                                              <div id="" class="trb_gptAd" data-role="adloader adloader_ad delayload delayload_done" data-state="adloader_unloaded"  data-withinviewport-options="bottomOffset=100&topOffset=1000000"  data-adloader-position="articleCubeCombo" data-adloader-size="300x250" data-adloader-adtype="cubecombo" data-adloader-label></div        >                                            <div class="trb_sharelines"  ><div class="trb_sharelines_list" data-role="socialshare_item"      ><a class="trb_shareline" data-role="socialshare_information socialshare_toggleState socialshare_container" data-socialshare-context="shareline" data-socialshare-url="/books/jacketcopy/la-et-jc-walter-dean-myers-an-appreciation-of-a-pioneer-20140702-story.html" data-socialshare-title="Walter Dean Myers was a pioneer of diversity in young adult books" data-socialshare-thumbnail="http://www.trbimg.com/img-53b49999/turbine/la-et-jc-walter-dean-myers-an-appreciation-of-a-pioneer-20140702" data-socialshare-description="Walter Dean Myers&apos; lifelong battle for a more diverse YA literature" data-socialshare-slug="la-et-jc-walter-dean-myers-an-appreciation-of-a-pioneer-20140702" data-socialshare-content="story" data-socialshare-newspapername="Los Angeles Times" data-socialshare-content-id="80706008"  data-socialshare-default-ima