g-54245ba0/turbine/la-ca-jc-heather-cox-richardson-20140928" data-content-url="/books/jacketcopy/la-ca-jc-heather-cox-richardson-20140928-story.html">                <a href="/books/jacketcopy/la-ca-jc-heather-cox-richardson-20140928-story.html#navtype=panel" data-role="delayload_item  delayload_done imgsize_item" class="trb_outfit_group_list_item_figure"><img itemprop="image" data-baseurl="http://www.trbimg.com/img-54245ba0/turbine/la-ca-jc-heather-cox-richardson-20140928" alt="&apos;To Make Men Free&apos; is a timely tale of the ever-changing GOP" class="trb_outfit_group_list_item_img" title="&apos;To Make Men Free&apos; is a timely tale of the ever-changing GOP" data-content-naturalwidth="1002" data-content-naturalheight="1500" /></a><section class="trb_outfit_group_list_item_body"                  ><div class="trb_outfit_group_item_label" data-content-label=""                    ><span class="trb_outfit_categorySectionHeading"><a class="trb_outfit_categorySectionHeading_a" href="/books/jacketcopy/#navtype=panel">Jacket Copy</a></span                    >&#32;<time class="trb_outfit_categorySectionHeading_date" datetime="2014-09-25T13:00:00PDT" data-datetime-timezone="PDT" data-datetime-month="September" data-datetime-monthShort="Sep." data-datetime-day="25" data-datetime-year="2014" data-datetime-weekday="Thursday" data-datetime-weekdayShort="Thu." data-datetime-fullclock="1:00:00 PM" data-datetime-clock="1:00 PM" data-datetime-hour="1 PM"  data-datetime-daydiff="-2 days left"></time>&#32;<span class="trb_outfits_metabuckets_3"></span                  ></div                  ><span class="trb_outfit_relatedListTitle"                    ><a href="/books/jacketcopy/la-ca-jc-heather-cox-richardson-20140928-story.html#navtype=panel"  class="trb_outfit_relatedListTitle_a">&apos;To Make Men Free&apos; is a timely tale of the ever-changing GOP</a><span class="trb_outfits_metabuckets"><span class="trb_outfits_metabuckets_1"></span></span                  ></span        